"<guimenuitem>Permissions</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Owner</guimenuitem> or "
"<guimenuitem>User Group</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"<guisubmenu>अन्य</guisubmenu> सबमेनू <guimenuitem>पथ</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>लिंक गंतव्य</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>कॉपी किया गया</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>अनुमतियाँ</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>स्वामी</"
"guimenuitem> या <guimenuitem>उपयोगकर्ता समूह</guimenuitem> का चयन करने की अनुमति "
"देता है।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folder View Properties"
msgstr "फ़ोल्डर दृश्य गुण"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following settings control how the contents of a folder are displayed in "
"the &konqueror; view, and are stored on a per-folder basis by default:"
msgstr ""
