#: index.docbook:1972
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Machine translation is not a perfect science! Google will at best give "
#| "you a rough translation, and at worst will give you a very funny read. "
#| "Don't base important decisions on things you have read from a Google "
#| "translated page, without confirming that the translation is indeed "
#| "accurate."
msgid ""
"Machine translation is not a perfect science! Google will at best give you a "
